{"tid":1881370,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國研究: 支那肺炎每位病人感染4.7~6.6人","createTime":"2020-02-15T13:30:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T01:31:49.000Z","uid":32511,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"15d7ee5e7e7e96267516f2b6caa0e059e804aa50","tid":1881370,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T13:30:06.000Z","msg":"美國洛斯阿拉莫斯國家實驗室，裡面的研究員們發表了論文的preprint，指出武漢病毒的R0在 4.7 到 6.6之間，也就是每個患者會感染 5 到 6 人，遠超過原先估計的 2.2 ~ 2.7，患者數在傳染初期每 2.4 天會翻倍<br />\n<br />\nAbstract<br />\n<br />\n... we estimated that the number of infected<br />\nindividuals during early epidemic double every 2.4 days, and the R0 value is<br />\nlikely to be between 4.7 and 6.6. We further show that quarantine and contact<br />\ntracing of symptomatic individuals alone may not be effective and early,<br />\nstrong control measures are needed to stop transmission of the virus.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2002.03268\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F2002.03268&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx4PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=e02f1f51\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2002.03268</a>"},{"pid":"d8dd12c9cebc8f8537e2f02fdb9c623c5dd05ed6","tid":1881370,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T13:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hNq74yi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhNq74yi.jpg&h=e153c784&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c44b3835e26b2ffcb606dbf19563932581ff2e9b","tid":1881370,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"現代版天花"},{"pid":"5cbabcd26c83baf8e030e2246cc69f75e12f6184","tid":1881370,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"cls..."},{"pid":"2d1cb771fbc931c37594020df77ecca3723350bf","tid":1881370,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T13:35:47.000Z",